info.description:
Flask-PyMssql
-------------

PyMssql support for Flask applications

Installation
============

Flask-PyMssql is pip-installable:

    pip install Flask-PyMssql

Development
===========

Source code is hosted in `GitHub <https://github.com/rchacon/flask-pymssql>`
